```json
{
  "application": "COBALT",
  "details": {
    "scheduler": "COBALT",
    "queue": "default",
    "nodes": "nNode",
    "time": "06:00:00",
    "project": "AtlasADSP",
    "memory": "mcdram=cache:numa=quad",
    "access_point": "{accessPoint}",
    "environment_variables": [
      "PROC_PER_NODE",
      "NUM_NODES",
      "ATHENA_PROC_NUMBER",
      "HARVESTER_DIR",
      "EXAMPLES_DIR",
      "PILOT_DIR",
      "YODA_DIR",
      "YAMPL_DIR",
      "YAMPL_PY_DIR",
      "RUCIO_ACCOUNT",
      "X509_USER_PROXY",
      "X509_CERT_DIR",
      "HPC_SW_INSTALL_AREA",
      "PYTHONPATH",
      "LD_LIBRARY_PATH",
      "WORK_DIR",
      "PANDA_JOB_IDS"
    ],
    "software_requirements": [
      "python",
      "aprun",
      "mpirun",
      "panda-yoda",
      "yampl",
      "python-yampl",
      "rucio-clients",
      "emi"
    ],
    "commands": [
      "python -V",
      "which aprun",
      "which python",
      "python -c \"import json;pids = json.load(open('worker_pandaids.json'));print ' '.join(str(x) for x in pids)\""
    ],
    "libraries": [
      "python",
      "yampl",
      "panda-yoda"
    ],
    "resources": {
      "cpu": "128",
      "memory": "quad numa nodes",
      "storage": "{accessPoint}"
    },
    "execution_style": {
      "parallel": "mpi",
      "tasks": "1 per node",
      "runtime_environment": "aprun"
    },
    "input_data": "worker_pandaids.json"
  }
}
```
